# Cinematic AI Video Portfolio

This is a showcase of my AI-generated cinematic video projects. All videos were written, structured, and edited by me using tools like Kling, CapCut, Filmora, and ChatGPT.

---

## Pompeii – Cinematic AI Disaster Story  
[▶ Watch Video](https://youtube.com/shorts/56we_nzOyCA?feature=share)  
**Description:**  
A hyper-realistic AI-generated reenactment of Pompeii’s final hours before the catastrophic eruption of Mount Vesuvius. This short film captures the tension, fear, and beauty of a city frozen in time — blending AI visuals, cinematic pacing, and historical storytelling.
